      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Clinical herbalist  ·  American Herbalist Guild (1400 hrs classroom + 200 hr practicum naturopath)\nChem + Botany — University of Iowa, 1982    Painted waves 38 years.\n22 years in Nosara.    Apothecary in town + US online.    Farm with 40+ fruit trees, grows from 5–7 AM only.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Clinical herbalist  ·  American Herbalist Guild (1400 hrs classroom + 200 hr practicum naturopath)\nChem + Botany — University of Iowa, 1982    Painted waves 38 years.\n22 years in Nosara.    Apothecary in town + US online.    Farm with 40+ fruit trees, grows from 5–7 AM only.",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "baseline": 13,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "a7"
    },
