      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Modern food overloads it.\nPreservatives · dyes · gums (xanthan/guar)\nstabilizers · seed oils · CR volcanic water\n(arsenic, mercury, lead)\n\nSIGNS of overload:\n→ flat AM belly, hard pouch by night\n→ afternoon crash, brain fog, want coffee\n→ dry/itchy skin (despite humidity)\n→ breakouts: face / shoulders / back",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Modern food overloads it.\nPreservatives · dyes · gums (xanthan/guar)\nstabilizers · seed oils · CR volcanic water\n(arsenic, mercury, lead)\n\nSIGNS of overload:\n→ flat AM belly, hard pouch by night\n→ afternoon crash, brain fog, want coffee\n→ dry/itchy skin (despite humidity)\n→ breakouts: face / shoulders / back",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "baseline": 13,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "b2"
