      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "INGREDIENTS:\n  Oregon grape · Milk thistle seed\n  Yellow dock · Dandelion\n  Burdock · Red root\n\nDOSE:  1 cap, 1–3× daily, with meals\nFEEL:  energy returns ~2 weeks\n\n\"Everyone should take it daily.\"\n— Catherine",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "INGREDIENTS:\n  Oregon grape · Milk thistle seed\n  Yellow dock · Dandelion\n  Burdock · Red root\n\nDOSE:  1 cap, 1–3× daily, with meals\nFEEL:  energy returns ~2 weeks\n\n\"Everyone should take it daily.\"\n— Catherine",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
