      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Minimal ≠ good.\nMore colors on plate = more nutrients.\n\nNEED:  deep dark greens (B vits)\n           fruits (vit C, riboflavin)\n           variety (no monotony deficiency)\n\nAVOID:  preservatives, dyes, gums,\n            stabilizers, seed oils",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
