      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Vodka 35–40% ≠ enough\nTerpenes need 96–98% alcohol\nOPERATING: 60–65%\n\nUS:  Everclear (200 proof) + distilled\n        water + hydrometer\nCR:  must distill your own\n        (cane sugar mash → 4% ferment →\n         reflux column → high ABV)\n\nVapor: alcohol 174°F  ·  water 200°F",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Vodka 35–40% ≠ enough\nTerpenes need 96–98% alcohol\nOPERATING: 60–65%\n\nUS:  Everclear (200 proof) + distilled\n        water + hydrometer\nCR:  must distill your own\n        (cane sugar mash → 4% ferment →\n         reflux column → high ABV)\n\nVapor: alcohol 174°F  ·  water 200°F",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
