      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "Every task has its window:\n  Seeds            19–26 of cycle\n  Prune bushier   17–25\n  Root cuttings    1–13\n  Cuttings           1–8\n  Air layering    24–28\n\nFULL + NEW moon ±2 days  =  REST\n→ right-time roots fast; wrong-time struggles\n\n\"Every farmer here knows this.\"",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Every task has its window:\n  Seeds            19–26 of cycle\n  Prune bushier   17–25\n  Root cuttings    1–13\n  Cuttings           1–8\n  Air layering    24–28\n\nFULL + NEW moon ±2 days  =  REST\n→ right-time roots fast; wrong-time struggles\n\n\"Every farmer here knows this.\"",
