      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "TOMATOES (same for papayas):\n1.  Squeeze seeds + water → jar\n2.  Ferment 3–4 days (seeds sink, smell)\n3.  Strain, wash, dry till crisp\n     (fermenting removes germ inhibitor)\n\nCUTTINGS (bougainvillea, etc.):\n  scrape bark + rooting hormone +\n  nutrient potting mix → bag/pot",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "TOMATOES (same for papayas):\n1.  Squeeze seeds + water → jar\n2.  Ferment 3–4 days (seeds sink, smell)\n3.  Strain, wash, dry till crisp\n     (fermenting removes germ inhibitor)\n\nCUTTINGS (bougainvillea, etc.):\n  scrape bark + rooting hormone +\n  nutrient potting mix → bag/pot",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
      "baseline": 13,
      "autoResize": true,
      "index": "bh"
