      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "RAISED BED MIX (her recipe):\n  compost · sand · charcoal · rice hulls\n  coconut coir · dirt · composted manure\n\nGUANACASTE = brutal:\n  Dec 15 → Apr 15  zero rain · 100°F\n  must irrigate everything\n  rainy → corrugated plastic roof\n  work 5–7 AM only (after = hot/buggy)",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "RAISED BED MIX (her recipe):\n  compost · sand · charcoal · rice hulls\n  coconut coir · dirt · composted manure\n\nGUANACASTE = brutal:\n  Dec 15 → Apr 15  zero rain · 100°F\n  must irrigate everything\n  rainy → corrugated plastic roof\n  work 5–7 AM only (after = hot/buggy)",
      "lineHeight": 1.4,
