      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "MORINGA  =  multivitamin tree\n  highest natural conc. of vits + minerals\n  eat leaf (bitter) · grows in CR\n  → Discovery Channel YouTube doc\n\nVETIVER  =  anti-landslide grass\nPAPAYA fruit  =  vit A + beta carotene\n   seeds  =  arsenic, TOXIC,\n               NOT a parasite cure\n40+ fruit trees on her farm",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
